{"tid":1086532,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得拍拖去到一個位一定有鐘意第二個人嘅時候","createTime":"2019-03-31T23:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T06:27:24.000Z","uid":87656,"like":11,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e76c79286d0887f031aef11b949e10f754056ff","tid":1086532,"uid":87656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T23:42:47.000Z","msg":"講緊拍長拖起碼幾年以上果啲<br />\n事源我女朋友話拍拖耐咗一定會淡<br />\n然後果段時間遇到合心意嘅人內心一定會對佢有好感<br />\n嚴重啲咁講就係內心出軌<br />\n只不過段感情繼唔繼續到就係睇你對份關係嘅忠心同尊重<br />\n我就覺得如果夠愛嘅話段關係唔會淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正評: 夠愛唔會淡, 唔會對人有好感<br />\n負評: 耐左點都會淡, 會對其他人有好感<br />\n<br />\n利申: 我女朋友好愛我(應該)"},{"pid":"af774638c676519cefc81df2efc08c6a3a898ec8","tid":1086532,"uid":53421,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T23:51:38.000Z","msg":"有 好感到搵d藉口飛埋我<br />\n<br />\n拍左13年了"},{"pid":"6d2d6ce490684bab4c8416bce349c7bc735d2d80","tid":1086532,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T23:52:25.000Z","msg":"屌厭左好正常"},{"pid":"899133ae42a4dfd1601bb9abd2635a4c99808a95","tid":1086532,"uid":188148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T00:00:36.000Z","msg":"唔會淡，但對其他人有好感"},{"pid":"a2454c0075d1f2e94c005059993506688ef61dda","tid":1086532,"uid":87656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af774638c676519cefc81df2efc08c6a3a898ec8","tid":1086532,"uid":53421,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T23:51:38.000Z","msg":"有 好感到搵d藉口飛埋我<br />\n<br />\n拍左13年了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T00:58:24.000Z","msg":"有冇得救?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拍咗咁耐都咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2940fb2f062a81aa9625dde6ee7709ca7c00d0d0","tid":1086532,"uid":53421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2454c0075d1f2e94c005059993506688ef61dda","tid":1086532,"uid":87656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af77